name: Book of Hollander Maui
description:
Hollander Maui shoots timeless impressionistic photos that capture the aura of a scene with his Focuso technique! Collect the first interactive book of beautiful bokeh.

Visit http://hollandermaui.com for the official Website. A YouTube introduction is here https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F22ATuOtjgs. The Retrospective Opening at the Focus Gallery is here https://youtu.be/EDxfLenpehY and a 3D video here https://youtu.be/eirpCbCsNaM.

The interactive book was made with the ZIM JavaScript Canvas Framework founded by Dr Abstract, who is the inaugural member of the Gadget Minters. To find out more please visit https://zimjs.com/gadgetminters and https://zimjs.com/nft for info on making interactive NFTs with ZIM.
